UserRepository implementation that retrieves user information. This method first checks the cache for the user record, then falls back to querying the database if not found.

impl UserRepository {
    pub async fn getUserById(&self, id: UserId) -> Option<User> {
        self.cache.get(&id).or_else(|| self.db.find_user(id))
    }
}

